        		'body'=>'<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large"><span style="background-color:#ffffff">When you come to Da Nang - a dynamic city, beside the fun activities in the beach, the historical places are also the great choice for your trip. One of that places is Da Nang museum.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large">Da Nang Museum is located in Dien Hai citadel, is in the heart of Da Nang city. This was a place where Da Nang people fighted to repel French troops in the early 1958. Therefore, it has been awarded certificate at the national level by the Ministry of Culture.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large">Da Nang Museum has a space of 3000 square meters. This place displays historical objects of our nation during the struggle against enemy invaders. Da Nang museum consist of three floors arranged&nbsp;very reasonably creating advantage for tourists&#39;s sightseeing:</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large">The first floor: Display artifacts about history and cultures of Da Nang people.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large">The second floor : Display historical artifacts about French and American resistance war of our nation. Beside, it also displays many pictures which denounce the crime of the enemy as well as displays artifacts about our nation&#39;s life in the war.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large">The third floors: Display artifacts about cultures of Viet Nam such as : Dong Son Culture, Sa Huynh Culture,.. This is also place for archaeologists research about culture of Viet Nam in historical periods.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large"><img alt="" src="/assets/images/posts/images/museum%202.jpg" /> </span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left"><span style="color:#222222"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,serif"><span style="font-size:large">Summary, Da Nang Museum is&nbsp; not only place where store historical document of&nbsp; Da Nang people but also is place to educate young generation about the tradition of fighting his father.</span></span></span></p>

