        		'body'=>'<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:13pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:#141414"><span style="font-size:14.0pt">Mention to Da Nang, probably many people will remember Han bridge, Dragon bridge, My Khe beach, Ba Na Hill, clean roads ...All make a city worth living in the eyes of friends in the country and internationally. But to make that success, we can not forget to mention Da Nang people.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:13pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:#141414"><span style="font-size:14.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Da Nang people</strong> are very friendly, hospitality. They always ready to help tourists when tourists want to find information about places or roads in the city. From small market trades to the polices, everyone is ready to help. They all want to make the tourists feel welcome here. Additionally, Da Nang people are known for diligence. They are very enduring, hard-working. They work hard to earn money to cover their family life. They always believe in the future.</span></span></span></span></p>

